core:masterGremlin.description:
{green|Master Gremlin}

Gremlins are indentured to menial labor around a Tower. While they are not great warriors by any standard, they are numerous and willing. Gremlins attack with their attached balls and chains. Master gremlins - those who have proven their loyalty - are cut from their balls and chains and able to hurl them in a ranged attack.

{gold|Special Ability : Ranged attack.}

core:stoneGargoyle.description:
{green|Stone Gargoyle}

Stone and Obsidian Gargoyles are demon-form statues animated for use as troops. They attack with raking claws.

{gold|Special Ability : Gargoyle}
Though Stone and Obsidian Gargoyles are considered as non-living, they are still affected by morale and mind spells.

core:obsidianGargoyle.description:
{green|Obsidian Gargoyle}

