core:ironGolem.description:
{green|Stone Golem}

Stone and iron golems are built and animated through a process involving both precise craftsmanship and complex magic. Though slow, they are strong and durable combatants.

{gold|Special Ability : Non-living. Spell damage reduction 50% .}
Stone golems take half damage from spell attacks, while iron golems take only a quarter of such damage.

core:stoneGolem.description:
{green|Iron Golem}

Stone and iron golems are built and animated through a process involving both precise craftsmanship and complex magic. Though slow, they are strong and durable combatants.

